sections.heading: consultant; license; violation; penalty
sections.text: No person shall act as an insurance consultant until he or she has been licensed as provided by sections 44-2606 to 44-2635. Any person violating this section shall be guilty of a Class IV misdemeanor.SourceLaws 1980, LB 481, ยง 10;Laws 1989, LB 92, ยง 206.
